    {
      "id": "PopularPost364954",
      "post_content": "Here's a flavorful (if not exactly efficient) combo with this: [Eon Hub](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eon Hub) takes away the upkeep, [Kismet](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kismet) (or [Frozen \u00c6ther](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Frozen \u00c6ther)) keeps your opponents from saving lands up, [Wheel of Sun and Moon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wheel of Sun and Moon) recycles your discards, and [Mana Short](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Short) begins the lockdown. Do this and you essentially freeze time. Forever. Just wait for them to deck out.  \n  \nOr (for the especially sadistic) give your opponent a wheel too, and Magic the Gathering turns into a game of \"Who can put up with sitting here doing nothing the longest?\"",
      "posted_by": "Gameguy602",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost364954\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Here's a flavorful (if not exactly efficient) combo with this: <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Eon Hub\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Eon Hub\">Eon Hub</a> takes away the upkeep, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Kismet\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kismet\">Kismet</a> (or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Frozen \u00c6ther\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Frozen \u00c6ther\">Frozen \u00c6ther</a>) keeps your opponents from saving lands up, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wheel of Sun and Moon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wheel of Sun and Moon\">Wheel of Sun and Moon</a> recycles your discards, and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mana Short\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Short\">Mana Short</a> begins the lockdown. Do this and you essentially freeze time. Forever. Just wait for them to deck out.<br/><br/>Or (for the especially sadistic) give your opponent a wheel too, and Magic the Gathering turns into a game of \"Who can put up with sitting here doing nothing the longest?\"</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '364954'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"Post